---
title: Quick Crumbed Chicken Strip Tacos with Charred Pineapple Salsa & Zesty Slaw
description: It’s the deliciousness of crumbed chicken wrapped up in a taco, it can’t get any better. Oh wait, it can because we’re
crumbing these chicken strips with a smokey Aussie spice mix. Add a splash of flavour with a pineapple salsa and these tacos are very hard to beat.
